  "name": "Vasana Farnan's Daughter",
  "notes": "Daughter of Farnan, slain by the Crimson Bat; scarred at Moonbroth. Natural born Ernaldori/Colymar leader, fearsome bison rider, and Orlanth Adventurous/Vinga future-initiation path. Strict ADR-0015 fixture: RQG initiate Rune magic is withheld at chargen; folio spirit magic and cult magic require GM conversion/advancement. Uses Molon's +3D6 damage bonus for lance charges. RQG folio Battle Axe is represented by Mythras Battleaxe. RQG folio spirit magic (Demoralize, Heal 2, Mobility) maps to Mythras Demoralise/Heal/Mobility (Mythras Core Rules p.122-130): Heal is present; Demoralise and Mobility are withheld under strict ADR-0015 because they are not in the general picker and require cult/GM advancement. See references/folk-magic-reconciliation.json \u00a7vasana_rqg_spirit_magic_mapping. Active passion values are reconciled to the app's strict chargen formula (54) rather than the higher RQG folio values; folio passion targets are preserved as identity evidence.",
